      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in impeccable condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a factory 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is mechanically flawless, having received a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, with all bushings and suspension geometry maintained to factory specifications. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth and interior surfaces are indistinguishable from new. A true purist\u2019s example with a fully documented service history.",
